      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SWEET LEGS (7) has a terrific record this track and trip with four wins and four placings from eight starts. Missed the frame latest (20.29) when seventh over 352m at Q Lakeside in a Grade 5. Expected to go close. CANYA CURRENCY (1) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing third behind Panama Power (16.86) in a Mix 5. Hard to beat again. FINNIS BALE (2) finds it hard to break through. Finished third (30.42) at Q Parklands latest and might be close to finding winning form again. Form from her last run is proving strong. Expected to be in this for a long way. STAYING ALIVE (8) was out of the money here last time out but can bounce back.",
